      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait how can more lithium prevent toxicity tho?? i thought if the levels get too high that's what causes the toxicity and makes things worse. i'm kinda scared to try anything if it's actually dangerous. if i'm feeling lightheaded and shaky, is it really just something i can fix by changing my dose myself?",
